@startuml
!theme handwritten

title 迭代器模式

interface Aggregate {
    Iterator iterator()
}

interface Iterator {
    boolean hasNext()
    T next()
}

class BookShelf {
    BookIterator iterator()
}

class BookIterator {
    BookShelf bookShelf
    boolean hasNext()
    Book next()
}

note top of Aggregate
    集合，用于创建Iterator迭代器接口
end note

note bottom of BookShelf
    会创建出具体的Iterator角色
end note

note bottom of BookIterator
    具体的迭代器，
    包含了遍历集合所必须的信息（bookShelf）
end note

Aggregate --> Iterator : Creates
BookShelf ..|> Aggregate
BookIterator ..|> Iterator
BookShelf o-- BookIterator

@enduml